      "parameters": {
        "content": "## FLOW 2: Find Doctors (live)\nGeocodes the user's postcode via Nominatim, queries OpenStreetMap (Overpass) for nearby doctors, normalizes the results, and responds with the list.",
        "height": 256,
        "width": 336,
